<p class=3D"">Wondering how to calculate the area of a trapezoid? Instead o=
f memorizing a formula blindly, help your child understand why it works =E2=
=80=94 it builds stronger math thinking.</p>



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" data=
