t=3D"39px" id=3D"toc_2_Rotate_and_combine_the_two_trapezoids">2. Rotate and=
 combine the two trapezoids</h3>



<p class=3D"">Now, rotate the copy and place it next to the original trapez=
oid, flipping it upside down so that the two shapes fit together perfectly.=
 What do you see?</p>


<div class=3D"wp-block-image">
<figure class=3D"aligncenter size-large is-resized"><img data-recalc-dims=
