<p class=3D"">The area of the trapezoid =3D =C2=BD =C3=97 (base=E2=82=81 + =
base=E2=82=82) =C3=97 height =3D =C2=BD =C3=97 (8 + 12) =C3=97 6 =3D 60</p>



<p class=3D"">The answer is 60.</p>



